(h) The Lead Center shall be open to the public twelve months each year, operating on a 40 hour week basis or during the
normal business hours of the recipient organization. Anticipated closures for holidays and other organizational
shutdowns shall be included in the annual application submitted by the SBDC. Emergency closures shall be reported
