 130.510


Transfer of funds.


(a) All SBDC Cooperative Agreements will be funded through the SBA internal ``Letter of Credit Replacement System''
(LORS), formerly administered under the Department of Treasury's Letter of Credit (LOC) system. The Standard Forms
1193A and 1194 will be used to establish and modify letters of credit.
